---
title: "Notes"
layout: "base.njk"
nav: true
menutitle: Notes
order: 4
pageDescription:  "<p class='maxcharacterlength--54'>Initial, exploratory reflections on music, PKM, design, and more.</p>"
---
<div>
     {% include "partials/_introduction.njk" %}
    <section>
        <ul class="notesgrid">
            {% if collections.notes.length > 0 %}
                {% for note in collections.notes %}
                <li>
                    <a class="notesgrid__link" href="{{ note.url }}">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="notesgrid__icon"><path d="M13.4 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-7.4"/><path d="M2 6h4"/><path d="M2 10h4"/><path d="M2 14h4"/><path d="M2 18h4"/><path d="M18.4 2.6a2.17 2.17 0 0 1 3 3L16 11l-4 1 1-4Z"/></svg>
                        <div class="noteinformation">
                            <span class="noteinformation__title">{{ note.data.title }}</span>
                            <span class="noteinformation__metadata smalltext">{{ note.data.category }} • {{ note.data.updated | readableDate }}</span>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </li>
                {% endfor %}
            {% else %}
            <li><strong>Here's where I'd put my notes. If I had any 😤.</strong></li>
        {% endif %}
        </ul>
    </section>
</div>